display_long_description:
Project Moose V3 is an adrenaline-fueled multiplayer tag experience that puts your reflexes and strategy to the test. Step into fast-paced arenas where the goal is simple—don’t get tagged! But in the world of Project Moose V3, nothing stays simple for long.

Run, jump, climb, and dodge your way through chaotic matches where every second counts. Whether you’re the hunter striking with moose-like speed or the runner desperately trying to escape, the tension never lets up. Quick thinking and sharp movement are the keys to survival.

With smooth controls, dynamic arenas, and an energetic community, Project Moose V3 delivers endless replayability. Will you outsmart your friends and prove yourself as the ultimate player, or will you get caught slipping?

Get ready to move fast, play hard, and charge like a moose.
